These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
2 different games are played: canasta, backgammon
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, rowing
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daffodil
1. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
2. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
3. the person who's sport is rowing is not the fan of reggae##6
4. the person who's sport is rowing is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
5. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##8
6. the thai is not the person who growsamaryllis##6
7. the person eating raspberry is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Game      | backgammon   | canasta      |
| Food          | strawberry | raspberry   |
| Sport         | rowing    | parkour |
| Pet           | chinchilla     | horse    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | reggae       |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai        |
| Flower     | amaryllis     | daffodil        |

