1. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
3. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person eating lemon##6
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |
| Birthday      | april | october        |
| Food          | lemon         | apricot       |
| Hobby         | drawing       | hiking        |
| Game           | bridge        | backgammon |
| Transport   | bus     | helicopter       |
| Pet   | rat       | dog       |
| Cigar         | baccarat      | alhambra    |

